Essar, Zimbabwe to Form Joint Ventures to Acquire ZISCO Steel. Mine Assets

-- B y   P r a d e e p   K u r u p
-- 
2011-03-10T09:48:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-10/essar-zimbabwe-to-form-joint-ventures-to-acquire-zisco-steel-mine-assets.html
Essar Africa Holdings Ltd. reached
an agreement with the government of  Zimbabwe  for two venture
companies to acquire steel and mining assets and liabilities of
Zimbabwe Iron & Steel Co. and its units, according to an e-
mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Pradeep Kurup at 
 pkurup3@bloomberg.net  